name: Pixl Coin
additional_notices: Kindly be aware that liquidity provided in Automated Market Maker platforms (eg. Uniswap, Sushiswap, Balancer) can be removed (also known as rug pulling), resulting in a collapse of available liquidity. Please exercise caution when trading! This notice is NOT directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder for our users.

description.en: The main use case of PIXL is the 1million Pixl advertising pad where other projects can advertise there logos etc by buying pixl space. The genius here is that they pay using PIXL that they will buy on the open market meaning price increases the more PIXL adverts are sold. None of these tokens will ever be sold so it creates an ever increasing price floor. Running alongside this will be the 8bit retro arcade bespoke to PIXL. It can also be used for banner adverts paid for with the PIXL coin!
